        <section class="three-bears-approach">
            <h2>Our Signature: The Three Bears Approach</h2>
            <p>Just like in the classic tale, we believe in finding the perfect fit for your individual needs. Our "Three Bears Approach" is built on three core principles:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Papa Bear Strength & Stability:</strong> We focus on building a strong and stable foundation through targeted exercises. This helps improve posture, support your body, and reduce the risk of future issues. We provide a robust plan that is appropriately challenging for your current abilities.</li>
                <li><strong>Mama Bear Movement & Mobility:</strong> We emphasize restoring and improving your range of motion and functional movement. Our programs are designed to be nurturing and progressive, helping you move with greater ease and comfort in your daily life.</li>
                <li><strong>Baby Bear Gentle Recovery & Adaptation:</strong> We understand the importance of gentle and gradual rehabilitation and adaptation. Whether you're recovering from an injury or learning to navigate a disability, our approach is patient, supportive, and tailored to your pace and comfort level.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our experienced personal trainer, will work closely with you to assess your unique situation and create a personalized plan that incorporates elements of all three "bears" to help you achieve your specific goals.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="specializations">
