            <ul>
                <li><strong>Posture Correction:</strong> Addressing imbalances for improved alignment and reduced discomfort.</li>
                <li><strong>Pain Management:</strong> Developing strategies to alleviate chronic pain through targeted movement and exercise.</li>
                <li><strong>Adaptive Training for Disabilities:</strong> Creating inclusive and effective fitness programs tailored to individual abilities.</li>
                <li><strong>Injury Rehabilitation:</strong> Guiding you through a structured and progressive recovery process (in collaboration with healthcare professionals).</li>
                <li><strong>Functional Movement Training:</strong> Enhancing your ability to perform everyday activities with greater ease and less pain.</li>
